Every Time You Want to Run the App:
You need exactly 2 terminals - one for backend, one for frontend.

Order matters:

âœ… Start backend FIRST (Terminal 1)
âœ… Then start frontend (Terminal 2)
âœ… Then open browser

ðŸ“‹ Step-by-Step Startup Instructions
Terminal 1: Backend Server
